we'll sit down and nobody will ever know."

00:25:44.400 --> 00:25:46.440
So, nobody ever needs to see you sweat.

00:25:46.440 --> 00:25:47.440
&gt;&gt;audience #7: Great.

00:25:47.440 --> 00:25:51.500
&gt;&gt;Ina: And if all else fails, there's always
