00:26:05.110 --> 00:26:06.110
[laughter]

00:26:06.110 --> 00:26:08.549
It's always something, and those are the best
parties.

00:26:08.549 --> 00:26:09.549
[laughter]

00:26:09.549 --> 00:26:14.799
So, you just have a good laugh about it and
nobody ever needs to know.

